  <releases>
    <release version="0.9.0" date="2026-05-21">
      <description>
        <p>
          First public testing release. Includes everything in the
          milestone build (M1–M8) plus the post-release expansion:
          adjustable reading-column width, master-detail Study Journal
          with tag management, module picker with language filter and
          per-module info, F11 reading-mode exit affordance, F3 /
          Shift+F3 search step-through with case toggle and match
          highlighting, Generic Books reader with TOC navigation, and
